      <title>英国首相抨击保守党抵制香港，呼吁与中国缓和关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/uk-peer-slams-tory-boycott-of-hong-kong-urges-thaw-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党资深人士彼得·曼德尔森 (Peter Mandelson) 指责前保守党政府未能与中国维持“适当的沟通渠道”，没有履行英国在香港的责任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/uk-peer-slams-tory-boycott-of-hong-kong-urges-thaw-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:58:06 GMT</pubDate>
