    <item>
      <title>格鲁吉亚总统呼吁选举联盟反对执政党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/georgia-president-urges-election-coalition-against-ruling-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚总统萨洛梅·祖拉比奇维利呼吁两股反对力量在议会选举中联合起来对抗执政党，她表示，这次选举将决定格鲁吉亚是加入欧盟还是重返俄罗斯轨道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/georgia-president-urges-election-coalition-against-ruling-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:42:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国代表团称委内瑞拉镇压是反人类罪行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/un-mission-says-venezuela-repression-was-crime-against-humanity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国报告称，委内瑞拉在7月大选后迫害异见人士，犯下了“反人类罪”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/un-mission-says-venezuela-repression-was-crime-against-humanity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:38:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>推动北以居民返回可能加剧紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/push-to-return-north-israel-residents-risks-inflaming-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列称，让因真主党袭击而流离失所的居民返回家园现在是一项正式的战争目标，这表明该国正在考虑对黎巴嫩激进组织发动全面进攻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/push-to-return-north-israel-residents-risks-inflaming-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:36:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰盟友开始考虑如何实现停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/ukraine-russia-ceasefire-kyiv-s-allies-start-to-look-at-how-it-could-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰的一些盟友开始谈论抵抗俄罗斯入侵的战斗将如何结束，这引发了其他几个西方国家首都的担忧，他们担心这些努力可能导致基辅被迫过早停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/ukraine-russia-ceasefire-kyiv-s-allies-start-to-look-at-how-it-could-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:21:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯洛伐克罢免反对党领袖，剥夺其议会重要职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/slovakia-ousts-opposition-leader-from-key-parliament-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克执政联盟将反对党领袖从议会副议长职位上撤职，此举引发外界指责，认为这是对总理罗伯特·菲科主要批评者的报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/slovakia-ousts-opposition-leader-from-key-parliament-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:13:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将在 LGBTQ 新战略中禁止扭转疗法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-to-pursue-ban-on-conversion-therapy-in-new-lgbtq-strategy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟首次承诺禁止转化疗法，这是欧盟委员会主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩计划在第二任期内推行的一项新的 LGBTQ 平等战略的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-to-pursue-ban-on-conversion-therapy-in-new-lgbtq-strategy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:03:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储准备降息之际，巴西央行行长立场鹰派</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/brazil-braces-for-hawkish-central-bank-chief-just-as-fed-readies-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行新权力掮客加布里埃尔·加利波罗 (Gabriel Galipolo) 在过去几周内彻底转型为反通胀斗士。加利波罗被任命为央行行长，此举颠覆了拉丁美洲最大经济体的货币政策前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/brazil-braces-for-hawkish-central-bank-chief-just-as-fed-readies-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙消防员和飞机在阿威罗地区遭遇火灾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/portuguese-firefighters-continue-to-face-blazes-in-aveiro-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去两天气温升高，消防员继续在阿威罗地区和葡萄牙北部其他地区扑灭大火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/portuguese-firefighters-continue-to-face-blazes-in-aveiro-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 08:16:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蒙特利尔败选后特鲁多面临更大离职压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trudeau-to-face-more-pressure-to-leave-after-montreal-defeat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多遭遇重大政治挫折，他领导的自由党在蒙特利尔一个选区的特别选举中落败，而直到最近，该选区还被认为是他的安全阵地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trudeau-to-face-more-pressure-to-leave-after-montreal-defeat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 07:08:13 GMT</pubDate>
